long_description: nahuen is a word from the traditional mapuche language of mapudungun, meaning strength/resilience and energy. we believe that music is harm reduction. nahuen offers community karaoke & audio rental, but is so much more then an audio rental business. more community services organization then audio rental company, at nahuen, we believe in the power of music and collective energy. passionate about community building and harm reduction, we aim to bring music, the universal language, to people and communities facing barriers. we would love to work with other service providers and community partners to help facilitate connection, community, and collective energy, by bringing music, the universal language, to your organization. we can host regular karaoke nights, open-mic nights, dj services, or one time events.
